caption.text:
.
Happy 17th, Dek.
.
My childhood's highlight was having you followed me everywhere and then we would have a bloody-fight (literally bloody: nosebleed) because you annoyed the heck out of me. Kerjaan jaman SD: nyisihin duit jajan buat beliin mainan buat kamu sama remon hanya untuk rusak seminggu kemudianüòí
Your teen's highlight was having me as 'the-super-annoying-and-crazy-and-LOUD' sister (ofc I always am) who followed you everywhere. Karma does exist, bro.
(But you still 'melorotin' me anywayüòí)
.
Kalo dipikir lagi, dari dulu kamu emang manja ya. Dari yang awalnya sekecil kutu, jadi setinggi tiang. Dari yang awalnya sekurus ilalang, masih kurus aja sih biarpun makannya sebakul (literally). Dari yang awalnya sering teriak kalo diganggu, jadi pasrah (dan balik menghina bahkanüòí). Dari yang awalnya berisik gak ketulungan, sekarang akhirnya tenang di samping Tuhanüòá
.
Cece pasti kangen bisa ejek kamu, gigit kamu (maaf kalo bekasnya susah ilang ya HEHE), maksain kamu ikut kemana2 dan ganggu sampe kamu teriak sebel. Sekarang juga tukang-foto-dadakan tersabar udah ga ada HAHA :( Seneng ya kamu ga ada yang menuhin memori hp lagi, minta gendong lagi, nabok sampe kulit merah lagiüò∞ And I lose my headlock partner!üí™üèª But you're already in the best place right now, so that's allright :)
.
I'm sorry for what happened. 
I'm sorry that you couldn't make it to your 17th, sorry that we couldn't do anything to make you stay. You're already on your own, Dek. Please be safe there :)
And we'll always be sorry that this world, all of us (your sisters, brother, family, friends), could not keep you safe anymore.
Maaf kalau kita semua ga bisa jaga kamu dengan baik ya, Dek. Sekali lagi maaf :(
.
Since your very first breath, 'till your very last one.
Since your very first cry, 'till your very last smile.
Since the day God gave you home, 'till the day God took you 'HOME'.
Please remember that we love you dearly,
in life and death.
.
In memoriam, our beloved brother,
Audi Wijaya.
23 Februari 2000 - 27 Januari 2017
